@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@authToken = <YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE>
@contentType = application/json

### 1. 계약 등록 (Register Contract)
POST {{baseUrl}}/contracts
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "carId": 1,
  "customerId": 1,
  "contractPrice": 35000000,
  "meetings": [
    {
      "date": "2024-12-25T14:00:00.000Z",
      "alarms": [
        "2024-12-24T14:00:00.000Z",
        "2024-12-25T09:00:00.000Z"
      ]
    }
  ]
}

### 2. 계약 목록 조회 (Get All Contracts)
# 검색 조건 예시: ?searchBy=customerName&keyword=홍길동
GET {{baseUrl}}/contracts?page=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### 3. 계약 수정 (Patch Contract)
# 담당자(작성자)만 수정 가능
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/contracts/1
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "contractPrice": 34000000,
  "meetings": [
    {
      "date": "2024-12-26T15:00:00.000Z",
      "alarms": [
        "2024-12-26T10:00:00.000Z"
      ]
    }
  ]
}

### 4. 계약 삭제 (Delete Contract)
# 담당자(작성자)만 삭제 가능
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/contracts/1
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### 5. 차량 목록 조회 (Get Car List)
# 계약 등록 시 선택할 차량 목록
GET {{baseUrl}}/contracts/cars
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### 6. 고객 목록 조회 (Get Customer List)
# 계약 등록 시 선택할 고객 목록
GET {{baseUrl}}/contracts/customers
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### 7. 담당자(유저) 목록 조회 (Get User List)
GET {{baseUrl}}/contracts/users
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}